      "seed": 4920183756,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 183920475,
      "updated": 1749000000000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Step 4: Dedup + Upsert\n\nDeduplicate by skill_key (repo::path)\nBulk upsert in batches of 500\nEnsure idx_skill_key unique index\nTotal: ~5-8 min runtime",
      "originalText": "Step 4: Dedup + Upsert\n\nDeduplicate by skill_key (repo::path)\nBulk upsert in batches of 500\nEnsure idx_skill_key unique index\nTotal: ~5-8 min runtime",
