      "updated": 1749000000000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "MongoDB Atlas  —  db: skillissue  ·  collection: github_skills  (~10K docs)\n\nIndexes: skill_key (unique) · stars (desc) · last_indexed (desc) · owner+stars\nWeighted text search: skill_name=10, owner=5, repo=3, description=1",
      "originalText": "MongoDB Atlas  —  db: skillissue  ·  collection: github_skills  (~10K docs)\n\nIndexes: skill_key (unique) · stars (desc) · last_indexed (desc) · owner+stars\nWeighted text search: skill_name=10, owner=5, repo=3, description=1",
