      "versionNonce": 293847105,
      "updated": 1749000000000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Data stored per skill: skill_key · skill_name · repo · file_path · folder_path · owner · owner_avatar · repo_description · stars · html_url · language · topics · last_indexed\nContent is never stored — the frontend fetches .md files directly from GitHub when a user opens a skill. This keeps the DB lightweight (metadata only).\nUser-uploaded skills (Appwrite) are a separate system — users sign in via Google OAuth, create skills in the SkillBuilder, and manage them in their profile.",
      "originalText": "Data stored per skill: skill_key · skill_name · repo · file_path · folder_path · owner · owner_avatar · repo_description · stars · html_url · language · topics · last_indexed\nContent is never stored — the frontend fetches .md files directly from GitHub when a user opens a skill. This keeps the DB lightweight (metadata only).\nUser-uploaded skills (Appwrite) are a separate system — users sign in via Google OAuth, create skills in the SkillBuilder, and manage them in their profile.",
